Name: RGBCELLS
About the game: RGBCELLS is a Puzzle Game . Your goal is to unlock all the Cells' color . Use the Big RGB Bar to scan , Red + Green = Yellow Red + Blue = Violet Green + Blue = Cyan What's the cell's color ? Then use the Small Color Bar to confirm your guess . In the style of Minesweeper . ▪ Custom Levels (∞) ▪ Steam Achievement (The Game won't end if you make the wrong decision, but I hope you don't use the Exhaustion to play) - Trading Card Coming Soon (Enabled if qualify) Powered by Unity 2D.
